#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.250"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.250:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.250:0.2"
msgid "25. Duccaritavagga"
msgstr "25. Bad Conduct"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.250:0.3"
msgid "250. Puggalappasādasutta"
msgstr "250. Faith in Individuals"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.270"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.250:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā puggalappasāde."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of placing faith in an "
"individual."

msgctxt "an5.250:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.250:1.3"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, bhikkhave, puggale puggalo abhippasanno hoti, so tathārūpaṃ āpattiṃ "
"āpanno hoti yathārūpāya āpattiyā saṅgho ukkhipati."
msgstr ""
"The individual to whom a person is devoted falls into an offense such that "
"the Saṅgha suspends them."

msgctxt "an5.250:1.4"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "It occurs to them:"

msgctxt "an5.250:1.5"
msgid "‘yo kho myāyaṃ puggalo piyo manāpo so saṅghena ukkhitto’ti."
msgstr "‘This person dear and beloved to me has been suspended by the Saṅgha.’"

msgctxt "an5.250:1.6"
msgid "Bhikkhūsu appasādabahulo hoti."
msgstr "They lose much of their faith in mendicants."

msgctxt "an5.250:1.7"
msgid "Bhikkhūsu appasādabahulo samāno aññe bhikkhū na bhajati."
msgstr "So they don’t frequent other mendicants,"

msgctxt "an5.250:1.8"
msgid "Aññe bhikkhū abhajanto saddhammaṃ na suṇāti."
msgstr "they don’t hear the true teaching,"

msgctxt "an5.250:1.9"
msgid "Saddhammaṃ asuṇanto saddhammā parihāyati."
msgstr "and they fall away from the true teaching."

msgctxt "an5.250:1.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo ādīnavo puggalappasāde."
msgstr "This is the first drawback in placing faith in an individual."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.250:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ puggale puggalo abhippasanno hoti, so "
"tathārūpaṃ āpattiṃ āpanno hoti yathārūpāya āpattiyā saṅgho ante nisīdāpeti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the individual to whom a person is devoted falls into an "
"offense such that the Saṅgha makes them sit at the end of the line. …"

msgctxt "an5.250:2.2"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.250:2.3"
msgid "‘yo kho myāyaṃ puggalo piyo manāpo so saṅghena ante nisīdāpito’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.250:2.4"
msgid "Bhikkhūsu appasādabahulo hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.250:2.5"
msgid "Bhikkhūsu appasādabahulo samāno aññe bhikkhū na bhajati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.250:2.6"
msgid "Aññe bhikkhū abhajanto saddhammaṃ na suṇāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.250:2.7"
msgid "Saddhammaṃ asuṇanto saddhammā parihāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.250:2.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo ādīnavo puggalappasāde."
msgstr "This is the second drawback in placing faith in an individual."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.250:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ puggale puggalo abhippasanno hoti, so "
"disāpakkanto hoti … pe … so vibbhanto hoti … pe … so kālaṅkato hoti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, the individual to whom a person is devoted departs for another "
"region … disrobes … passes away."

msgctxt "an5.250:3.2"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "It occurs to them:"

msgctxt "an5.250:3.3"
msgid "‘yo kho myāyaṃ puggalo piyo manāpo so kālaṅkato’ti."
msgstr "‘This person dear and beloved to me has passed away.’"

msgctxt "an5.250:3.4"
msgid "Aññe bhikkhū na bhajati."
msgstr "So they don’t frequent other mendicants,"

msgctxt "an5.250:3.5"
msgid "Aññe bhikkhū abhajanto saddhammaṃ na suṇāti."
msgstr "they don’t hear the true teaching,"

msgctxt "an5.250:3.6"
msgid "Saddhammaṃ asuṇanto saddhammā parihāyati."
msgstr "and they fall away from the true teaching."

msgctxt "an5.250:3.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo ādīnavo puggalappasāde."
msgstr "This is the fifth drawback in placing faith in an individual."

msgctxt "an5.250:3.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā puggalappasāde”ti."
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks of placing faith in an individual.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.250:3.9"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.250:3.10"
msgid "Duccaritavaggo pañcamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.271"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.250:4.1"
msgid "Duccaritaṃ kāyaduccaritaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.250:4.2"
msgid "Vacīduccaritaṃ manoduccaritaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.250:4.3"
msgid "Catūhi pare dve sivathikā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.250:4.4"
msgid "Puggalappasādena cāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an5.250:4.5"
msgid "Pañcamo paṇṇāsako samatto."
msgstr ""
